name: OxygenSaturationRate
title: Oxygen Saturation Rate
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains tests that measure peripheral capillary oxygen saturation for patients receiving care from EMS professionals.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients whose peripheral capillary oxygen saturation was measured while they received care from EMS professionals. . Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element would map to the Assessment category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include procedures and tests that measure peripheral capillary oxygen saturation, including blood gas measurement, oxygen saturation measurement, and pulse oximetry measurement.),(Exclusion Criteria: None)
